General Information

New Schick Intuition Island Berry Acai Berry Extract, lather & shave in one step!

Skin Moisturising Solid (Moisturises during shaving.)

Boxed Contents: 6 x 10g Skin Moisturising Solid (moisturises during shaving)

Size: 6 Pack

Scent: Acai Berry Extract

Warnings

Blades are sharp tools, handle with care. Keep away from children.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

All Schick Intuition cartridges are interchangeable. Try all of skin conditioning formulas.

Ingredients

Sodium Palmitate, Sodium Cocoate, Sodium Isostearate, Aqua Potassium Palmitate, Glycerin, Sodium Isostearoyl Lactylate, Potassium Cocoate, Potassium Isostearate, Kaolin, Parfum Sucrose Cocoate, Titanium Dioxide Sodium Chloride, PEG-50 Shea Butter, Pentasodium Pentetate, Tetrasodium Etidronate, Isostearic Acid, Euterpe Oleracea Fruit Oil, Hexyl Cinnamal, Linalool, CI 17200.

Directions

1 Attach Cartridge. 2 Add Water. 3 Shave!

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
